import { Button } from "@chakra-ui/button";
import { Flex, Text } from "@chakra-ui/layout";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

export default function Nav() {
  return (
    <Flex
      p="23px"
      background="#FFFFFF"
      alignItems="center"
      justifyContent="space-between"
      w="100%"
      m="0 auto"
      maxW="1367px"
    >
            <Text 
            justifyContent="flex-start"
            color="#FDC921" 
            ml="10px"
            fontSize="22px"
            fontWeight="900"
            
            >
            GoTokens
            </Text>
        <Flex>
            <Text 
            color="#454545" 
            mr="20px" 
            fontWeight="500"
            
            >
                Quem somos
            </Text>
            <Link to="/Login">
                <Button
                _hover={{}}
                width="89px"
                height="35px"
                background="#fff"
                boxShadow="0px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19)"
                borderRadius="45px"
                >
                Logar
                </Button>
            </Link>
        </Flex>
    </Flex>
  );
}
